<h2 id="group-api-design">Group API Design</h2>

<p>Now, itâ€™s time for you to think about your API.</p>

<ul>
  <li>What endpoints will you be offering?</li>
  <li>How will you handle authentication?</li>
  <li>How will you render relationships?</li>
</ul>
